entries.quest_location_d: 'Ord Mantell is known for having lienent baking laws. Anyone can get a bank account on Ord Mantell with no questions asked. Needless to say, the planet is very popular with smugglers and other underground denizens.'
entries.quest_patrol_d: 'Sulale Kallor was able to escape by hyperspacing out. I'll need to make sure that the immediate area is safe and free of Black Sun enemies.'
entries.split_quest_alert: Aleas Rans'ery: <Pilot! Black Sun vessels are coming to yer location!>
entries.title: The Return Home
entries.title_d: Return to the Tansarii Point Station and communicate with it to land. You can communicate with the Station by targeting it and typing /comm in spatial chat.
